            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The compiled cross sections are revised in p.301 of",
                "INDC(GER)-0053 by F.Kaeppeler. However, the revisions",
                "are not implemented in this EXFOR entry because of",
                "the following two reasons:",
                "   (1) 586+-9 mb is given as kT~25 keV gold SACS in",
                "       the 'Actual data' table, but 681/648=1.051 is",
                "       given as correction for revised gold standard",
                "       in the 'Revised data' table.",
                "   (2) 681 mb is given as kT~25 keV gold SACS in the",
                "       'Revised data' table, but it is kT=25 keV",
                "        gold MACS."
              ]
            }
